# Abstract

This document defines the shared terminology, notation, naming conventions, and
conformance language used throughout the Kapnet proposal family. Its purpose is
to reduce ambiguity across specifications concerning serialization, replay,
ordering, execution, anchoring, markets, namespaces, and interoperability.

# Copyright

